      <section id="section_ihj_53s_lcc">
         <title>General</title>
         <p>Bump cap, safety glasses, hearing protection, long sleeves, steel toed safety shoes.</p>
         <p>Have available a respirator with certified cartridges, or a PAPR, in case of a silica
               release or toxic batch material spill.</p>
